questionsAndAnswers.question: What you need from me to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Wix, Wordpress or Shopify login details Logo - Content - Typography - Color Scheme - Website sample you like - Any images/videos (Not necessary) If you don't have anything, don't worry, just contact me.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer any support after order completion?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes I offer free support after order completion for 30 days

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you get your order fast?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, you can. Please mention that you need it done fast when placing your order.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I be able to edit myself after delivery ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes of course. You will be able to edit yourself. In that case if you face any issue, I will help you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you also do Logo design ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, you need to purchase gig extra for logo. We will provide you multiple concepts for logo and will send all source files of your selected logo.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Are you able to provide Web hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, with an extra cost of $70 USD per year for the web hosting.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Are you able to create exact same design of link provided?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we can do exact clone of your provide design,

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you help me with website Content like (images)?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we will provide you paid stock images for your website in high quality.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you guide or discuss on zoom?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we can guide about everything on Zoom meeting

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you work on wordpress, wix, shopify website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes i can do work on wordpress, wix, shopify website. i have experience on these platforms and i have strong portfolio, if you want to check my portfolio please let me in chat.

reviews.comment: Zee was very patient with me in regards to sending him information to create my website. He was very kind and delivered what I expected. Thank you sooo much
I enjoy working with Zee on all my website and design needs. I can count on her to get the job done.
She did a good job executing on my directions and given informations. And executed my vision really well! Would definitely work with them again
👍🏽 Bit of a difficult project to deliver, but happy with the persistence overall.
Always a pleasure to work with

reviews_snippet.comment: E la prima volta che mi sono trovato a collaborare con Zee e devo dire che sono rimasto pienamente soddisfatto. Sin dall’inizio ha capito esattamente le mie esigenze e lavorando in maniera efficace ha portato un risultato finale che davvero mi lascia contento di aver fatto questa scelta. Qualora qualcuno necessitasse l’aiuto per la parte di grafica e web design, contattando Zee non potrà che rimanere super soddisfatto. Grazie ancora dell’ottimo lavoro svolto, sono sicuro che avremo modo di collaborare nuovamente in futuro.
Working with Zee continues to help move my business along in areas where I would lose time. Well worth investing in help to get things done faster.

Zeeshan is an excellent graphic designer. I had first used his services to create my logo and since then have given him multiple projects to work on like my website, my posters and my menus. Excellent communication and reliable. Brilliant service I can not recommend him enough. He has truly helped my vision come to life.
It was a pleasure working with Zeeshan, he did an excellent job creating the exact logo I was looking for. 10/10.

I have never tried Fiverr before and I needed a logo built. zeeshan152 did an excellent job and completely over delivered on this project! Thank you so much! This is going to help me get my online website up and running fast! Thanks again!
